Package Users

Class User

java.lang.Object
Users.User
Direct Known Subclasses:
Doctor, Patient
public abstract class User extends Object

User class

The User class is the super class of Patient and Doctor. It Contains shared attributes and methods. Since it is an abstract class, no object can be instantiated.

Author:
Max Endres, Harris Nuhanovic
